description:
Implement elapsed time tracking and display:

State:
- m.startTime time.Time (set when run starts)

Calculation (on each tick):
elapsed := time.Since(m.startTime)

Formatting:
- Under 1 hour: MM:SS (e.g., '5:23')
- Over 1 hour: H:MM:SS (e.g., '1:23:45')

func formatDuration(d time.Duration) string {
    h := int(d.Hours())
    m := int(d.Minutes()) % 60
    s := int(d.Seconds()) % 60
    if h > 0 {
        return fmt.Sprintf("%d:%02d:%02d", h, m, s)
    }
    return fmt.Sprintf("%d:%02d", m, s)
}

Display in status bar:
'Time: 5:23' with dim label, bright value

Updates every tick (1 second) automatically via tickMsg.
